<h1 class="nhsuk-heading-xl">Contact &amp; get involved</h1>

<p class="nhsuk-lead-paragraph">
  We want to hear from NHS trusts considering partnership, digital delivery partners, clinicians,
  and — most importantly — people living with sickle cell disease and their families.
</p>

<h2 class="nhsuk-heading-l">Who we’d like to hear from</h2>
<ul class="nhsuk-list nhsuk-list--bullet">
  <li><strong>NHS acute trusts</strong> delivering sickle cell and acute care, interested in hosting the pilot.</li>
  <li><strong>Digital delivery agencies</strong> interested in the <a class="nhsuk-link" href="{{ '/tender/' | url }}">tender</a>.</li>
  <li><strong>Patients, families and the sickle cell community</strong> — your experience shapes this.</li>
  <li><strong>Clinicians</strong> in haematology and emergency medicine.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="nhsuk-heading-l">Get in touch</h2>
<p class="nhsuk-body">
  Email the programme at
  <a class="nhsuk-link" href="mailto:carl.reynolds@nhsrho.org">carl.reynolds@nhsrho.org</a>,
  contact the {{ site.owner }} via <a class="nhsuk-link" href="https://www.nhsrho.org/">nhsrho.org</a>,
  or open an issue in the <a class="nhsuk-link" href="{{ site.repoUrl }}">project repository</a>.
</p>
